### Login Passenger

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "dev@test.com",
"password": "StrongPassword123!"
}

###

### Get Current User

GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

###

### Update Name

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Dev Updated"
}

###

### Try Updating Email

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"email": "[hacker@test.com](mailto:hacker@test.com)"
}

###

### Try Updating Role

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
"role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### Missing Token

GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
